(401, 1, '2013-01-19 21:23:56', '2013-01-19 21:23:56', '<strong>1. CHECKING ORDER STATUS:</strong>\r\n\r\nTIDE &amp; POOL will send you a confirmation email once we receive your order. When your order has shipped, we will send you an additional email that includes the UPS tracking number for your package. Please note that it may take up to 48 hours after your package has been shipped by tideandpool.com for the tracking information to appear in the UPS system. Upon receiving shipping confirmation, you may visit http://www.ups.com/tracking/tracking.html to verify order status.\r\n\r\nIf you have further inquiries, please email customerservice@tideandpool.com and we will do our best to help.\r\n\r\n<strong>2. CANCELLATIONS:</strong>\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, once an order is submitted, we are unable to change or cancel the order.Â  Please see the RETURNS section for more information on our return and exchange policies.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions about your order, please feel free to contact us at customerservice@tideandpool.com or (562) 277-1382 during our business hours of 9:30 AM â€“ 5:30 PM PST.Â  If we miss you, we will get back to you as soon as possible.\r\n\r\n<strong>3. PAYMENT METHODS:</strong>\r\n\r\ntideandpool.com accepts the following credit cards: American Express, Visa and MasterCard.Â  Credit cards must have a U.S. billing address. tideandpool.com does not accept cash, checks, or money orders.\r\n\r\n<strong>4. USING A PROMOTION CODE:</strong>\r\n\r\nFrom time to time, TIDE &amp; POOL may have special offers that can be applied to orders by using a promotion code. In order to take advantage of these promotions, please enter the promotional code in the space provided on the â€œOrder Reviewâ€ page and click â€œApplyâ€ before you place your order. The value of the promotion will be applied to your order and appear in the â€œDiscountâ€ field.\r\n\r\n<strong>5. SALES TAX</strong>\r\n\r\nA 9% sales tax will be applied to the product total on all orders shipped within California. Residents in other states are responsible for complying with the tax laws that apply to online purchases in their respective states.\r\n\r\n<strong>6. CREATING A TIDE &amp; POOL ACCOUNT</strong>\r\n\r\nWhen making a purchase on tideandpool.com you can become a TIDE &amp; POOL account holder by registering with your email address and a password. With an account, you can save time on future visits by storing shipping and billing information for a faster and easier checkout process. Any information you provide is kept secure and will never be sold to outside parties. TIDE &amp; POOL account holders can also find out about exclusive offers, special events and our latest designs by signing up for the TIDE &amp; POOL Swim Club mailing list.\r\n\r\n<strong>7. TO RETRIEVE YOUR TIDE &amp; POOL ACCOUNT PASSWORD</strong>\r\n\r\nTo retrieve your TIDE &amp; POOL account password, click on the â€œForgot Your Passwordâ€ link located below the account holder sign in during checkout.Â  Your password will be sent to your registered email address within minutes.\r\n\r\n<strong>8. GIFT OPTIONS</strong>\r\n\r\nFor gift items purchased at tideandpool.com we offer a complimentary gift card, which can be personalized with your own message, as well as a gift receipt. Just select your preferred gift option at checkout.\r\n\r\n<strong>9. CARE INSTRUCTIONS Â </strong>\r\n\r\nTIDE &amp; POOL towels are designed with enduring quality in mind. With proper care our vibrant designs will be a part of many sunny days to come.\r\nMachine-wash your towel on cold and before first use.\r\nTumble dry your towel at a low temperature.\r\nAvoid using fabric softener. It can reduce your towelâ€™s absorbency.\r\nDo not bleach or dry clean your towel.\r\nOur fiber reactive dyes resist fading caused by chlorine, salt water and exposure to sunlight during regular use. However, please do not store your towels in direct-sunlight.\r\n\r\n<strong>10. TIDE &amp; POOL SWIM CLUB EMAIL SIGN-UP</strong>\r\n\r\nIf you choose to receive email updates from tideandpool.com, weâ€™ll keep you in the loop on exclusive offers, special events and our latest sunny day essentials.\r\n\r\nYou do not need to open a TIDE &amp; POOL account to receive emails from us. You may sign up for our TIDE &amp; POOL Swim Club mailing list by clicking on the â€˜SWIM CLUBâ€™ link within the header of every page on tideandpool.com. Alternatively, you can subscribe to the mailing list by entering your email address in the field located at the bottom of every page.\r\n\r\nPlease note that you may unsubscribe from our mailing list at any time by clicking the â€œUnsubscribeâ€ link found at the bottom of all emails.', 'Ordering', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ordering', '', '', '2013-01-19 21:25:53', '2013-01-19 21:25:53', '', 0, 'http://local.tideandpool.com:8888/?p=401', 0, 'post', '', 0),
