(411, 1, '2013-01-19 21:30:16', '2013-01-19 21:30:16', '<strong>21. HOW CAN I CHECK THE STATUS OF MY ORDER?</strong>\r\n\r\nTIDE &amp; POOL will send you a confirmation email once we receive your order. When your order has shipped, we will send you an additional email that includes the UPS tracking number for your package. Please note that it may take up to 48 hours after your package has been shipped by tideandpool.com for the tracking information to appear in the UPS system. Upon receiving shipping confirmation, you may visit http://www.ups.com/tracking/tracking.html to verify order status.\r\n\r\nIf you have further inquiries, please email customerservice@tideandpool.com and we will do our best to help.\r\n\r\n<strong>22. HOW DO I CANCEL MY ORDER?</strong>\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, once an order is submitted, we are unable to change or cancel the order.Â  Please see the RETURNS section for more information on our return and exchange policies.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions about your order, please feel free to contact us at customerservice@tideandpool.com or (562) 277-1382 during our business hours of 9:30 AM â€“ 5:30 PM PST.Â  If we miss you, we will get back to you as soon as possible.\r\n\r\n<strong>23.Â  HOW CAN I EXCHANGE A GIFT I RECEIVED?</strong>\r\n\r\nIf you received a gift from tideandpool.com and would like to exchange it or receive store credit, please contact customer service at customerservice@tideandpool.com or (562) 277-1382.\r\n\r\n<strong>24.Â  HOW CAN I RETRIEVE MY TIDE &amp; POOL ACCOUNT PASSWORD?</strong>\r\n\r\nTo retrieve your TIDE &amp; POOL account password, click on the â€œForgot Your Passwordâ€ link located below the account holder sign in during checkout.Â  Your password will be sent to your registered email address within minutes.\r\n\r\n<strong>25.Â  DO I NEED A TIDE &amp; POOL ACCOUNT TO MAKE AN ONLINE PURCHASE?</strong>\r\n\r\nNo.Â  You may checkout without creating a TIDE &amp; POOL account.Â  Simply click the â€œContinueâ€ button to continue as a guest. TIDE &amp; POOL accounts are useful for storing address and billing information as well as expediting future shopping experiences on tideandpool.com.\r\n\r\n<strong>26. DOES TIDE &amp; POOL TAKE TELEPHONE ORDERS? Â </strong>\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, at this time we do not take orders by phone. You may only order at tideandpool.com.\r\n\r\n<strong>27. HOW CAN I PURCHASE MORE THAN THREE TOWELS OF THE SAME DESIGN?</strong>\r\n\r\nIf you would like to purchase more than three towels of the same design please contact us at customerservice@tideandpool.com or (562) 277-1382 and we will do our best to accommodate your request.\r\n\r\n<strong>28. WHICH CREDIT CARDS DOES TIDEANDPOOL.COM ACCEPT?</strong>\r\n\r\ntideandpool.com accepts American Express, Visa and MasterCard.Â  Credit cards must have a U.S. billing address.\r\n\r\ntideandpool.com does not currently accept cash, checks or money orders.\r\n\r\n<strong>29. DOES TIDEANDPOOL.COM CHARGE SALES TAX?</strong>\r\n\r\nA 9% sales tax will be applied to the product total on all orders shipped within California. Residents in other states are responsible for complying with the tax laws that apply to online purchases in their respective states.\r\n\r\n<strong>30. HOW DO I RECEIVE WEB PROMOTIONS OR SPECIAL OFFERS?</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be notified about special offers and promotions, please sign up for the TIDE &amp; POOL Swim Club mailing list.Â  Simply sign up by clicking on the â€˜SWIM CLUBâ€™ link within the header of every page on tideandpool.com. Alternatively, you can subscribe to the mailing list by entering your email address in the field located at the bottom of every page.\r\n\r\n\r\nIn order to take advantage of these promotions, please enter the promotional code in the space provided on the â€œOrder Reviewâ€ page and click â€œApplyâ€ before you place your order. The value of the promotion will be applied to your order and appear in the â€œDiscountâ€ field.\r\n\r\n<strong>31. HOW DO I CARE FOR MY TIDE &amp; POOL TOWELS?</strong>\r\n\r\nTIDE &amp; POOL towels are designed with enduring quality in mind. With proper care our vibrant designs will be a part of many sunny days to come.\r\nMachine-wash your towel on cold and before first use.\r\nTumble dry your towel at a low temperature.\r\nAvoid using fabric softener. It can reduce your towelâ€™s absorbency.\r\nDo not bleach or dry clean your towel.\r\nOur fiber reactive dyes resist fading caused by chlorine, salt water and exposure to sunlight during regular use. However, please do not store your towels in direct-sunlight.\r\n\r\n<strong>32. WHERE DOES TIDE &amp; POOL MANUFACTURE ITS MERCHANDISE AND IS IT ENVIRONMENTALLY COMPLIANT?</strong>\r\n\r\nTIDE &amp; POOL towels are produced in Brazil, a country known for its stunning coastline, lively beach culture and beautiful textiles. In the textile business for over 120 years, our manufacturer combines a century of craftsmanship with modern innovations in production techniques and sustainable manufacturing. Like TIDE &amp; POOL, they have an ongoing commitment to the responsible use of our natural resources and have been awarded the Fritz Muller Trophy for their environmental management system four times.', 'FAQs', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'faqs', '', '', '2013-01-19 21:30:16', '2013-01-19 21:30:16', '', 0, 'http://local.tideandpool.com:8888/?p=411', 0, 'post', '', 0),
